# Deliverables

## 1.

Create

```
resources/views/components/sections/industry-solutions.blade.php
```

Responsible for:

- section wrapper
- heading
- intro
- grid
- CTA
- spacing

---

## 2.

Create

```
resources/views/components/industry/card.blade.php
```

Responsible for one solution card.

Props should include:

```
title

description

image

icon

href

alt

featured (optional)

theme (optional)
```

No business logic.

Presentation only.

---

## 3.

Replace original homepage markup

Replace:

```
Industry Solutions
...
large static block
```

with

```
<x-sections.industry-solutions
    :solutions="$solutions"
/>
```

where

```
$solutions
```

remains a local array inside the homepage view.

No controllers.

No services.

No models.

No database.

---

